high_descs: Turn right and walk up to the window, then turn left and walk up to the counter.
Pick up the egg off of the counter.
Turn left and begin walking across the room, then turn left and walk up to the sink.
Put the egg in the sink basin then turn on the water, after a couple seconds turn the water off and take the now clean egg out of the sink.
Turn right and begin walking across the room, then hang a right and walk up to the green bin next to the counter.
Put the clean egg into the green bin.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean egg in a green bin.

high_descs: Move right to the counter top to the right of the stove
Pick up the egg on top of the counter top
Carry the egg over to the kitchen sink
Place the egg in the sink to wash the egg then pick it up again
Turn right then move to the green trash can
Place the egg inside of the green trash can
anns.task_desc: Move an egg to the green trash can

high_descs: Move to the counter top area between the range on the left and the wall on the right.
Pick up the white egg to the right of the lettuce from the counter top.
Turn to the left, move toward the brown door, then turn to the left and face the sink.
Wash the egg in the sink using water from the faucet, let the water drain, and pick up the egg from the sink.
Turn to the right, move past the red coffee maker, the turn to the right and move to the green recycling bin at the end of the counter.
Place the egg in the recycling bin to the rear of the apple.
anns.task_desc: Place a washed egg in the recycling bin.

high_descs: Move to the counter right of the stove.
Pick up the egg from the counter.
Bring the egg to the sink.
Place the egg into the sink and turn on the water.
Pick up the egg from the sink and bring it to the recycling bin.
Put the egg into the recycling bin.
anns.task_desc: Put the egg into the recycling bin.

high_descs: Turn right and walk to the window, then turn left and walk to the counter.
Pick up the egg on the counter.
Turn left and walk across the room, then turn left and walk to the sink.
Place the egg in the right side of the sink next to the spoon, rinse and remove egg.
Turn right, walk across the room, turn right and walk to the trash bin.
Place the egg in the trash bin.
Turn right, walk towards the window, turn left towards the lettuce.
Pick up the egg next to the lettuce.
Turn around and walk towards the sink.
Place the egg in the sink to wash it and pick up the egg.
Turn around and walk towards the recycling bin.
Place the egg in side the bin to the top right corner.
anns.task_desc: Place the washed egg inside the recycling bin.
